### Create a Pod
POST http://localhost:8080/pods
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My AI Knowledge Base",
  "ownerUserId": "raghav-123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("podId", response.body.id);
    client.log("Pod ID: " + client.global.get("podId"));
%}

### Add Data Item 1
POST http://localhost:8080/pods/{{podId}}/data
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Raghav is a Senior Software Engineer at Google DeepMind working on Agentic AI."
}

### Add Data Item 2
POST http://localhost:8080/pods/{{podId}}/data
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "The Social Distro project demonstrates scalable hexagonal architecture with Spring Boot 3."
}

### Trigger Indexing (Fan-out)
POST http://localhost:8080/indexing/pods/{{podId}}

> {%
    client.global.set("jobId", response.body.jobId);
    client.log("Job ID: " + client.global.get("jobId"));
%}

### Check Job Status
GET http://localhost:8080/indexing/jobs/{{jobId}}

### Query the Pod (RAG + Vector Search)
POST http://localhost:8080/pods/{{podId}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Where does Raghav work?"
}
